comments: Having signed up just to say this, in short, if you really want to learn the material, get in this class. Not an easy class, but if you\'re anything like me you\'ll be motivated by her enthusiasm. She cares greatly about her students and about her subject and will go to great lengths to reach out and inspire her class. Just be prepared to work hard

This is the best teacher in the world! It is a lot of work, but so worth it! As the class went on, she reasoned with the students and gathered input from what we think. She was so enthusiatic about teaching and made it worth while to be there.
She is the most enthusiastic, intelligent instructor I have ever had. You will never regret enrolling in one of her classes.
She rocks. Always use your socialogical imagination.

Best class I have ever taken and very well taught! I would recommend Carolyn Gates to anyone who wants to learn something interesting. Wonderful teaching style and best attitude, it would be impossible to fall asleep in this class!
I love the in class discussions!!
Fun and dedicated teacher. Wish all my teachers cared as much about my learning. I am certainly getting my monies worth and more.

Carolyn is the best teacher I have had at Cascadia. I can come to her with questions and if I email her I get a response back fast. If I\'m having a problem I know I can go to her and get adivce or help. Carolyn is the best!! I would defantly recomend taking Sociology from Carolyn.
